cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with the application of neural networks in image recognition and security, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The issue of vulnerability to adversarial examples also relates to the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the use of rotation as a defense mechanism involves the manipulation of images, which is a topic in the sub-category of neural networks (cs.NE).
